5|$|Critical {{reaction}} was generally favourable, with reviewers being {{impressed by the}} beauty of the graphics and the thrilling depiction of speed. They were however, slightly disappointed with the shallow nature of the gameplay. A newer version of <b>the</b> <b>arcade</b> game was released in 2003, incorporating motion simulator technology into <b>the</b> <b>arcade</b> cabinet.|$|E
