5|$|Indiana Jones and the Temple of Doom is {{an action}} game {{released}} in 1988 for the Nintendo Entertainment System. The game {{is based on}} <b>the</b> <b>arcade</b> game and film of the same name. The resulting product differed from <b>the</b> <b>arcade</b> version in several aspects, but kept the same underlying premise and style.|$|E
